author: dreid
msg: - add start of a new way of handling the IIS data for committers
Moving away from using too much dynamic content in favour of static content dynamically
generated at regular intervals. This is more inline with how we do the other websites
and keeps the development process more straightforward and quicker.
I've tried to make the entire process as configurable as possible, and have a few more
ideas that should be implemented at some point.
More to follow. This isn't live yet.
